# Smart Tourist Safety Monitoring & Incident Response System

Build the **Safety Hub** web platform and the **Eastern Sojourner Auth** mobile app, with Post-Quantum Cryptography (PQC) architecture, biometric security, and geo-fencing.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Scope Clarification**: This plan implements a fully functional front-end demo ecosystem with a local Node.js backend. The QRNG and ML-DSA (PQC) components are architected as **clearly documented placeholders** — pluggable when hardware/library support is available. No actual quantum hardware is needed.

> [!WARNING]
> **New directories will be created**: `safety/` (web), `auth-app/` (mobile), and `backend/` (Node.js server) — all inside the existing `Eastern Sojourner` project root.

---

## Proposed Changes

### Component 1: Safety Hub Web Platform (`/safety`)

The web pages will replicate the Eastern Sojourner dark theme (Inter font, indigo-purple gradients, glassmorphism cards, Tailwind CDN) and share the Netflix-style navigation bar.

#### [NEW] [index.html](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/safety/index.html)
- Safety Hub landing page with hero section
- "Connect Your Digital ID" CTA button
- Overview of safety features (Geo-fencing, SOS, Blockchain ID)
- Shared navbar with "Destinations" dropdown + active "Safety Hub" link
- Links to `/safety/connect.html` and `/safety/dashboard.html`

#### [NEW] [connect.html](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/safety/connect.html)
- **Connect Digital ID** page
- Generates a QR code (via `qrcode.js` CDN) containing a server-issued nonce
- Displays QR code with instructions to scan via the Auth app
- Polls backend (`/api/verify-status/:nonceId`) for signature verification result
- Shows success/failure status with animated transitions

#### [NEW] [dashboard.html](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/safety/dashboard.html)
- **Safety Dashboard** — only accessible after Digital ID is verified
- **Geo-fence Map**: Leaflet.js map displaying Northeast India with configurable geo-fence zones (safe/caution/restricted), tourist position marker
- **SOS Incident Response Panel**: Emergency button, incident type selector, auto-captures GPS + timestamp, sends alert payload
- **Active Alerts Feed**: Live-updating panel showing recent safety incidents
- **Tourist Status Card**: Shows verified Digital ID info, current zone status

#### [NEW] [safety.css](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/safety/safety.css)
- Safety Hub-specific styles extending the existing design system
- Map container styles, SOS button pulse animation, dashboard grid layout
- Status indicator animations (safe=green, caution=amber, danger=red)

#### [NEW] [safety.js](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/safety/safety.js)
- QR code generation (calls backend for nonce, renders with qrcode.js)
- Polling logic for verification status
- Leaflet map initialization with geo-fence polygon layers
- SOS button handler with payload construction
- Dashboard data refresh logic

