### Component 3: Eastern Sojourner Auth Mobile App (`/auth-app`)

React Native / Expo mobile application.

#### [NEW] [auth-app/](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/auth-app/)
- Scaffolded with `npx create-expo-app@latest ./`
- Key dependencies: `expo-local-authentication`, `expo-camera` (barcode scanner), `expo-secure-store`, `expo-location`, `react-native-get-random-values`

#### [NEW] [App.js](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/auth-app/App.js)
- Root component with navigation between screens
- Global context for authentication state and key pair

#### [NEW] [screens/BiometricGate.js](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/auth-app/screens/BiometricGate.js)
- **Biometric Identity Gate** — requires FaceID or Fingerprint before proceeding
- Uses `expo-local-authentication` for `authenticateAsync()`
- Shows branded splash with Eastern Sojourner logo
- Blocks all cryptographic operations until biometric is verified

#### [NEW] [screens/ScanScreen.js](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/auth-app/screens/ScanScreen.js)
- QR code scanner using `expo-camera`
- Extracts nonce data from scanned QR code
- Triggers biometric re-verification before signing
- Calls `signNonce()` then POSTs to backend `/api/verify`

#### [NEW] [screens/StatusScreen.js](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/auth-app/screens/StatusScreen.js)
- Displays verification result (success/failure)
- Shows signed payload details

#### [NEW] [utils/crypto.js](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/auth-app/utils/crypto.js)
- Key pair generation (ECDSA P-256) stored via `expo-secure-store`
- `signPayload(payload, privateKey)` — Signs concatenated `userId + nonce + gps + timestamp`
- **ML-DSA / PQC placeholder**: Extensive comments documenting hybrid signing architecture where both classical ECDSA and post-quantum ML-DSA signatures are generated side-by-side

#### [NEW] [utils/api.js](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/auth-app/utils/api.js)
- API client for communicating with the backend
- `postVerification({ nonceId, userId, signature, publicKey, gps, timestamp })`

