### Component 4: Security Documentation

#### [NEW] [SECURITY_RESEARCH.md](file:///c:/Users/TinasheHando/Documents/Eastern%20Sojourner/SECURITY_RESEARCH.md)
- **Threat Model** — Classical attacks (MITM interception, replay, signature forgery)
- **Replay Protection** — One-time nonce burn mechanism with TTL
- **Integrity** — Full payload signing (userId + GPS + timestamp)
- **PQC Readiness** — How ML-DSA placeholders protect against quantum threats to ECDSA
- **QRNG Architecture** — Why quantum entropy matters and the pluggable design
- **Burp Suite Testing Guide** — How to intercept and test all endpoints
- **Biometric Security** — Device-local biometric verification model

